\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup sugar\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup water\
{\listtext	\'95	}12 dried black mission figs\
{\listtext	\'95	}3 tablespoons {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/brandy/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 brandy}} or apple juice\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/hazelnut/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 hazelnuts}}, toasted * see Cook's Note\
